cc:Work.dc:title: Kuhn poker game tree

cc:Agent.dc:title: based on the graph in: Finnegan Southey, Bret Hoehn, Robert C. Holte. Effective short-term opponent exploitation in simplified poker, available at http://poker.cs.ualberta.ca/publications/AAAI05.pdf

cc:Work.dc:description: Full graph of the game states of Kuhn poker, together with mixed-strategy Nash equilibrium probabilities. Dotted subtrees represent dominated strategies.
